@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_refjqp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.21 - tmp + 0.35) - tmp) * wp.exp((v0 + 0.73 / tmp + 0.81)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.05) - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.45) - (v0 + 0.49 + v2 + 0.62)))
    v1 = (0.85 / (v2 * (v1 + 0.47 - v0 + 0.51)))
    v2 = (v1 - (wp.abs(v1 + 0.99) / wp.sin(v0 + 0.84)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.sin((tmp + 0.79 + v1 + 0.52)))
    v1 = v2
    v2 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
